## Data Flow: Telemetry Ingestion

```mermaid
flowchart TD
{% for s in sensors.edr %}
    EDR{{ loop.index }}["{{ s.hostname_short }}"] -->|telemetry| LC["LimaCharlie Cloud"]
{% endfor %}
    WH["Webhook Adapter"] -->|events| LC
{% for s in sensors.cloud %}
{% if s.is_online %}
    CLOUD{{ loop.index }}["{{ s.hostname }}"] -->|events| LC
{% else %}
    CLOUD{{ loop.index }}["{{ s.hostname }}<br/>(disabled)"] -.->|disabled| LC
{% endif %}
{% endfor %}

    LC --> DRE["D&R Engine"]
    DRE --> MATCH{"Rule Match?"}
    MATCH -->|Yes| DET["Generate Detection"]
    MATCH -->|No| STORE["Store in Insight<br/>(queryable via LCQL)"]
    DET --> CASES["ext-cases"]
    DET --> TRIG["AI Agent Trigger"]
    DET --> OUT["Outputs"]
```

