## Data Flow: {{ team.display_name }}

```mermaid
flowchart TD
{% for agent in team.agents %}
{% if agent.schedule %}
    SCHED_{{ loop.index }}["{{ agent.schedule }}"] --> {{ agent.key | replace('-', '_') }}["{{ agent.key }}<br/>model: {{ agent.model }} | budget: ${{ agent.budget }}"]
{% endif %}
{% endfor %}
{% for agent in team.agents %}
{% if not agent.schedule and agent.trigger_type == 'tag' %}
    TAG_{{ loop.index }}["tag: {{ agent.trigger_detail }}"] --> {{ agent.key | replace('-', '_') }}["{{ agent.key }}<br/>model: {{ agent.model }} | budget: ${{ agent.budget }}"]
{% elif not agent.schedule and agent.trigger_type == 'mention' %}
    MENTION_{{ loop.index }}["mention: {{ agent.trigger_detail }}"] --> {{ agent.key | replace('-', '_') }}["{{ agent.key }}<br/>model: {{ agent.model if agent.model else '—' }}"]
{% endif %}
{% endfor %}
```
